PTT2 BBS
ptt2.csie.ntu.edu.tw:3003

load maple2.board
setv postsign 1

=message
wait \e[1;33;46m★
till \e[37;45m\x20
till \x20\e[m
exit

=talk
call main
send t\n
wait 聊天說話
till 扣機

=talk_users
call talk
send u\n
wait 休閒聊天
  or 好友列表
till (TAB/f)

=query_user
call talk_users
send /
wait 代號：
send $[id]\n
send q
wait 《ＩＤ暱稱》
till 繼續
send \x20
exit 

=main
send \e[D\e[D\e[D\e[D\e[D\e[D
wait 主功能表
till 扣機

=talk_users_refresh
send \x15
wait 休閒聊天
  or 好友列表
till (TAB/f)
exit

=message_send
call talk_users
send /
wait 代號：
send $[receiver]\n
wait $[receiver]
send w
wait Call-In
send $[message]\n
wait [Y/n]
send \n
exit
